{"tid":1482353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個月過去，你地仲未明咩係冷氣軍師。","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:34:43.000Z","uid":270154,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca09e4eaf55e7a72b00485b2a923b36c962cba4f","tid":1482353,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師，<span style=\"color: red;\">軍師</span>呀嘛。<br />\n<br />\n將現場資訊、交通消息、逃生路線等資訊統一、整理，<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門、重覆回應，務求示威隨時看見。<br />\n<br />\n咁先係軍師呀嘛，呀哥。<br />\n<br />\n而唔係入所有熱門現場post都係充斥住，又送、又戀戰、開盤睇下又送幾多頭呀嘛。<br />\n<br />\n眾軍師都隔住個moon睇波，咁現場示威入黎睇你地睇波做乜呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔港屌我分化架啦，你地想幫場運動就改，唔想就繼續一群廢老咁。"},{"pid":"6f523e812602a19a030b9184910bd65a228af8ec","tid":1482353,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"［海外文宣新方向］激起各國本土意識 抵制中國貨及中資企業<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1482245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc94eaf31dc21ad9d08f9133814786043c587e14","tid":1482353,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"c9459960f33a7f8fecf259f38289041d629ca8f7","tid":1482353,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:15:53.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"4309a9960aba332b52e4a36c0ccab7ef913f7f47","tid":1482353,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"85bbbb9c92d460357ac5c0138714a91a1608e7e2","tid":1482353,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx